  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the MASS2 is to characterize accelerometer signals of Micra implantable
      device during different postures and activities and to understand the source of the sensed
      motion, in order to test feasibility for future enhancements in device functionalities.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
